bGWWAx-s6.memHandModelNotes: Elevational parameters vary, Palmer-Ball (1996) min in TN is 1600ft (487m), Klaus & Buehler (2001) 730 -1460m range in NC, Hamel (1992) occurance range is 300m-1500m. Went with liberal elevation range.  Confer (1992) identified that territorial boundaries extended 5-30m from open area into forest.  Also Klaus & Buehler (2001) identify slope parameters for NC as ranging from 13-37 degrees which could be to restricted so again, went liberal and just exlcuded flat summits, slope bottoms. Amy Silvano 6jun05
